    <string name="display_driving_mode">在屏幕上显示所选驾驶模式</string>
    <string name="display_driving_mode_desc">在平板屏幕上显示所选驾驶模式，包括自定义模式</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_normal_desc">适合日常驾驶的平衡设置：标准牵引力和舒适转向。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_comfort_desc">平顺的牵引力和轻盈的转向，带来轻松舒适的旅程。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_eco_desc">燃油/能源效率：油门响应平顺，换挡积极。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_dynamic_desc">运动响应：更灵敏的油门、更长的档位保持和更重的转向。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_sport_plus_desc">增强运动模式：最大响应速度和保持低档位（可用性取决于车型）。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_power_desc">最大性能模式：动力系统提供最大牵引力（混动车型中为内燃机和电动机联合驱动）。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_adaptive_desc">自适应模式：根据驾驶风格和路况自动选择经济/舒适/运动模式；在混动车型中，还会决定何时启动内燃机。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_custom_desc">自定义模式：保存您对牵引力、转向和悬架（如有）的偏好设置。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_pure_desc">纯电模式：内燃机仅在高负载或低电量时启动。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_hybrid_desc">默认混动模式：系统自动平衡内燃机和电动机，以优化牵引力和能效。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_save_desc">Battery preservation: maintains battery level at a set value (PHEV "hold" mode).</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_eco_hev_phev_desc">混动经济模式：优先使用电力驱动，响应平顺，空调功率适中，以达到最低能耗。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_phev_desc">Plug-in hybrid mode: focuses on hybrid logic (battery maintenance/discharge); on some models, identical to "Hybrid".</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_awd_desc">永久全轮驱动/离合器预紧：在湿滑路面上提供稳定性和牵引力。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_eawd_desc">电动四驱：通过电动机驱动后轴，实现即时牵引力和稳定性。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_offroad_desc">越野模式：针对不平坦地形重新配置牵引力、传动和稳定系统。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_snow_desc">雪地/冰面模式：柔和的油门、平顺的起步和增强的牵引力控制。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_sand_desc">沙地模式：保持速度并允许车轮打滑以避免陷车。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_mud_desc">泥地模式：增加低端牵引力并允许一定程度的打滑以保持动力。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_rock_desc">岩石模式：在低速攀爬时提供极其平顺的牵引力输出。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_hdc_desc">陡坡缓降控制：通过对单个车轮制动，在陡坡上保持低速行驶。</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_start_type_desc">Service start preset (calibration/diagnostics); not a user mode.</string>
    <string name="drive_mode_xc_desc">Internal designation (no public description); likely off-road/long-distance calibration.</string>
    <string name="function_status_disclaimer">Even if a function has a negative status, it may remain operational and supported. Similarly, a positive status does not always guarantee the function\'s correct operation. The status reflects how the system classifies the current function. The actual functionality must be verified experimentally.</string>
